    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1902-09-06T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1902-09-06T00:00:00-05:00" n="76"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d76">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">
                        <gloss type="from">King of the Belgians</gloss> to the <gloss type="to"
                            >President</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bagnères de Luchon</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-09-06">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 6, 1902</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Am glad that you escaped from the serious accident by which you have been
                    menaced; beg you to accept my most sincere and cordial congratulations.</p>
                <closer>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">King of the Belgians.</hi>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
